{
  "stem": "14168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I called from there, and I called my relatives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had relatives in Berlin, and one of my aunts said, why don't you come and stay with me?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In order not to be found out and arrested by the Gestapo, we went to a movie house in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I still remember the movie that we saw about Bengali-- B-E-N-G-A-L-I-- a British movie.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked down the main street of West Berlin, [GERMAN], just like Fifth Avenue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there had been the beautiful Jewish-- A beautiful temple, Fasanenstrasse, F-A-S-A-N-E-N-S-T-R-A-S-S-E, which was one of the pride of the Jewish community in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in ashes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I still remember an old man-- not-- a non-Jew, it must have been-- I'm sure he was not Jewish-- with a cane, standing in front of that-- the ashes-- glimmering ashes, shaking his head and said, what a shame for Germany.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I stayed with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had two aunts in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she did not live too far from the German Reich Chancellery, on Wilhelmstrasse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I tried to call my home, but from a public phone so they wouldn't find out who-- where I was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, [BACKROUND NOISE] one day, I was called by a relative of mine in Berlin, my aunt who lived in Spandau-- S-P-A-N-D-A-U.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She said, I have to talk to you, but you-- I must ask you to summon up all your strength.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I knew that something-- some terrible news was in store for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She said-- she was already-- she was in her 70s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She said, you need all your [NON-ENGLISH] that you can summon up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Your father has been killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, where?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We understand in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
